<h1>POKEMON TOOLS - IV CALCULATOR</h1>

<p>This tool will calculate all the possible IVs of a Pokemon given its EVs=
, Level, species and nature. A Pokemon that has just been caught has all it=
s EVs at 0. Since Diamond and Pearl, your Pokemon's <a href=3D"https://www.=
psypokes.com/dp/characteristics.php">characteristic</a> can also help deter=
mine which IV is the highest, and each game offers IV judges that can help =
narrow down IVs of each stat further.</p>

<p><b><i>Please note</i></b> that some Pokemon have received changes to the=
ir base stats since Generation 6. This tool automatically uses the current =
base stats as of Generation 9's Scarlet and Violet. If you are playing an o=
lder game, you can select the appropriate title in the Generation dropdown =
menu underneath your Pokemon selection.</p>

<p>Additionally, please note that IVs and DVs are not the same thing; IVs h=
ave been featured since Generation 3, while DVs are used in Generations 1 a=
nd 2. Click <a href=3D"https://www.psypokes.com/gsc/dv.php">here</a> to go =
to the DV Calculator.</p>



